  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't, and probably I'm glad-- I'm glad I didn't just-- I think it would've been real easy to commit mayhem.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It would have been real easy to, to do things that you shouldn't do, which would have lowered us to the same level of these people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- they went into Weimar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They brought out men, women, and children all dressed in their Sunday finest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They took them through the entire tour, just like I had been through, through the stacks of the bodies, into the-- into the organ room, into the crematoriums with the bodies still inside the ovens.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "To-- and they had taken-- there were-- there were no bodies laying around like when we first got there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had cleaned up that part.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there were stacks of bodies, of thousands of bodies, 1,000, 1,500, 2,000.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't have any idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the smell was just as bad as it was, if not worse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They went through the-- which was-- which is an isolation ward, an isolation section where these men that I told you about that-- where, where the excrement was so thick on the floor that you, you, you couldn't avoid stepping in it.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and these people were still alive, and they couldn't get away, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, they could not-- they were ex-- they were having bowel movements on each other, and they couldn't do-- they couldn't do-- they couldn't walk away from it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I can't imagine anything worse than that except physical death maybe, I don't know, torture or something, to be that helpless.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
